### openai-ollama-proxy API quick tests
### Requires VS Code REST Client extension
### Adjust @host if running on a different address

@host = http://localhost:11434

### Health check (HEAD)
HEAD {{host}}/ HTTP/1.1

###

### Health check (GET)
GET {{host}}/ HTTP/1.1

###

### Version
GET {{host}}/api/version HTTP/1.1

###

### List models (tags)
GET {{host}}/api/tags HTTP/1.1

###

### Running models (ps)
GET {{host}}/api/ps HTTP/1.1

###

### Show model info
POST {{host}}/api/show HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3:latest"
}

###

### Chat (non-streaming)
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3:latest",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Say hello in one sentence."}
  ],
  "stream": false
}

###

### Chat (streaming, default)
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3:latest",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "What is 2+2? Answer briefly."}
  ]
}

###

### Chat with thinking enabled
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3:latest",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "What is the square root of 144? Think step by step."}
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "think": true
}

###

### Chat with options (temperature, max tokens)
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3:latest",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Write a haiku about proxies."}
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "options": {
    "temperature": 0.9,
    "num_predict": 50,
    "top_p": 0.95
  }
}

###

### Chat with JSON format
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3:latest",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Return a JSON object with keys 'name' and 'age' for a fictional character."}
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "format": "json"
}

###

### Chat with tool calling
POST {{host}}/api/chat HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3:latest",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "What is the weather in San Francisco?"}
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "tools": [
    {
      "type": "function",
      "function": {
        "name": "get_current_weather",
        "description": "Get the current weather for a location",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "location": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "The city and state, e.g. San Francisco, CA"
            }
          },
          "required": ["location"]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}

###

### Embed (new endpoint)
POST {{host}}/api/embed HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3:latest",
  "input": "Hello, world!"
}

###

### Embeddings (legacy endpoint)
POST {{host}}/api/embeddings HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "qwen3:latest",
  "prompt": "Hello, world!"
}
